{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":528,"text":"What would be a good end of life?"},{"time":4116,"text":"And I'm talking about the very end."},{"time":6106,"text":"I'm talking about dying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9839,"text":"We all think a lot about how to live well."},{"time":13596,"text":"I'd like to talk about increasing our chances of dying well."},{"time":18028,"text":"I'm not a geriatrician."},{"time":20148,"text":"I design reading programs for preschoolers."},{"time":22852,"text":"What I know about this topic"},{"time":24678,"text":"comes from a qualitative study with a sample size of two."},{"time":29080,"text":"In the last few years, I helped two friends"},{"time":31785,"text":"have the end of life they wanted."},{"time":34026,"text":"Jim and Shirley Modini spent their 68 years of marriage"},{"time":37354,"text":"living off the grid on their 1,700-acre ranch"},{"time":40328,"text":"in the mountains of Sonoma County."},{"time":42419,"text":"They kept just enough livestock to make ends meet"},{"time":46343,"text":"so that the majority of their ranch would remain a refuge"},{"time":49650,"text":"for the bears and lions and so many other things"},{"time":51883,"text":"that lived there."},{"time":53490,"text":"This was their dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55503,"text":"I met Jim and Shirley in their 80s."},{"time":58786,"text":"They were both only children who chose not to have kids."},{"time":62267,"text":"As we became friends, I became their trustee"},{"time":64846,"text":"and their medical advocate,"},{"time":66675,"text":"but more importantly, I became"},{"time":68683,"text":"the person who managed their end-of-life experiences."},{"time":72442,"text":"And we learned a few things about how to have a good end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76115,"text":"In their final years, Jim and Shirley"},{"time":78086,"text":"faced cancers, fractures, infections, neurological illness."},{"time":82086,"text":"It's true."},{"time":83159,"text":"At the end, our bodily functions"},{"time":85396,"text":"and independence are declining to zero."},{"time":88177,"text":"What we found is that, with a plan and the right people,"},{"time":91331,"text":"quality of life can remain high."},{"time":94885,"text":"The beginning of the end is triggered"},{"time":96324,"text":"by a mortality awareness event, and during this time,"},{"time":99215,"text":"Jim and Shirley chose ACR nature preserves"},{"time":103453,"text":"to take their ranch over when they were gone."},{"time":105985,"text":"This gave them the peace of mind to move forward."},{"time":109565,"text":"It might be a diagnosis. It might be your intuition."},{"time":113041,"text":"But one day, you're going to say, \"This thing is going to get me.\""},{"time":116257,"text":"Jim and Shirley spent this time"},{"time":117813,"text":"letting friends know that their end was near"},{"time":119816,"text":"and that they were okay with that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124872,"text":"Dying from cancer and dying from neurological illness"},{"time":127721,"text":"are different."},{"time":129292,"text":"In both cases, last days are about quiet reassurance."},{"time":133594,"text":"Jim died first. He was conscious until the very end,"},{"time":137353,"text":"but on his last day he couldn't talk."},{"time":139540,"text":"Through his eyes, we knew when he needed to hear again,"},{"time":141653,"text":"\"It is all set, Jim. We're going to take care of Shirley"},{"time":144489,"text":"right here at the ranch,"},{"time":145658,"text":"and ACR's going to take care of your wildlife forever.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":149487,"text":"From this experience I'm going to share five practices."},{"time":152179,"text":"I've put worksheets online,"},{"time":153994,"text":"so if you'd like, you can plan your own end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156777,"text":"It starts with a plan."},{"time":159244,"text":"Most people say, \"I'd like to die at home.\""},{"time":161761,"text":"Eighty percent of Americans die in a hospital"},{"time":163986,"text":"or a nursing home."},{"time":165490,"text":"Saying we'd like to die at home is not a plan."},{"time":169145,"text":"A lot of people say, \"If I get like that, just shoot me.\""},{"time":172362,"text":"This is not a plan either; this is illegal."},{"time":174858,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":178912,"text":"A plan involves answering"},{"time":181739,"text":"straightforward questions about the end you want."},{"time":184097,"text":"Where do you want to be when you're no longer independent?"},{"time":186794,"text":"What do you want in terms of medical intervention?"},{"time":189691,"text":"And who's going to make sure your plan is followed?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":192065,"text":"You will need advocates."},{"time":193542,"text":"Having more than one increases your chance"},{"time":195173,"text":"of getting the end you want."},{"time":196933,"text":"Don't assume the natural choice is your spouse or child."},{"time":199513,"text":"You want someone who has the time and proximity"},{"time":201838,"text":"to do this job well, and you want someone"},{"time":204429,"text":"who can work with people under the pressure"},{"time":206668,"text":"of an ever-changing situation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209029,"text":"Hospital readiness is critical."},{"time":210723,"text":"You are likely to be headed to the emergency room,"},{"time":212627,"text":"and you want to get this right."},{"time":214406,"text":"Prepare a one-page summary of your medical history,"},{"time":217269,"text":"medications and physician information."},{"time":219557,"text":"Put this in a really bright envelope"},{"time":221831,"text":"with copies of your insurance cards, your power of attorney,"},{"time":224667,"text":"and your do-not-resuscitate order."},{"time":227067,"text":"Have advocates keep a set in their car."},{"time":228689,"text":"Tape a set to your refrigerator."},{"time":230576,"text":"When you show up in the E.R. with this packet,"},{"time":232811,"text":"your admission is streamlined in a material way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236534,"text":"You're going to need caregivers."},{"time":239139,"text":"You'll need to assess your personality and financial situation"},{"time":242769,"text":"to determine whether an elder care community"},{"time":245793,"text":"or staying at home is your best choice."},{"time":248192,"text":"In either case, do not settle."},{"time":250899,"text":"We went through a number of not-quite-right caregivers"},{"time":254265,"text":"before we found the perfect team"},{"time":256865,"text":"led by Marsha,"},{"time":259104,"text":"who won't let you win at bingo just because you're dying"},{"time":265826,"text":"but will go out and take videos of your ranch for you"},{"time":268402,"text":"when you can't get out there,"},{"time":270828,"text":"and Caitlin, who won't let you skip your morning exercises"},{"time":273555,"text":"but knows when you need to hear"},{"time":275161,"text":"that your wife is in good hands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278753,"text":"Finally, last words."},{"time":281380,"text":"What do you want to hear at the very end,"},{"time":282731,"text":"and from whom would you like to hear it?"},{"time":285339,"text":"In my experience, you'll want to hear"},{"time":287666,"text":"that whatever you're worried about is going to be fine."},{"time":291668,"text":"When you believe it's okay to let go, you will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295620,"text":"So, this is a topic that normally inspires fear and denial."},{"time":301490,"text":"What I've learned"},{"time":303596,"text":"is if we put some time into planning our end of life,"},{"time":306531,"text":"we have the best chance of maintaining our quality of life."},{"time":309945,"text":"Here are Jim and Shirley just after deciding"},{"time":312525,"text":"who would take care of their ranch."},{"time":314997,"text":"Here's Jim just a few weeks before he died,"},{"time":318357,"text":"celebrating a birthday he didn't expect to see."},{"time":321731,"text":"And here's Shirley just a few days before she died"},{"time":325749,"text":"being read an article in that day's paper"},{"time":327760,"text":"about the significance of the wildlife refuge"},{"time":330085,"text":"at the Modini ranch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332341,"text":"Jim and Shirley had a good end of life,"},{"time":335094,"text":"and by sharing their story with you,"},{"time":337527,"text":"I hope to increase our chances of doing the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340382,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341669,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}